DialogueNode.dialogue: Hey Dave
Hey Player!
How was your weekend?
Could I ask you a few questions about something?
Sure, what's up?
Well, I've been looking into some reports of sexual discrimination. Do you happen to have any information about that?
Not bad, had a date night with the wife. How was yours?
Good, good. Relaxing.
Not bad, but could've been better. I was working on some stuff.
Sorry to hear that. Were you working on anything specific?
Good to hear! Well, unless you need anything from me, I should probably be getting back to work
Alright, talk to you later, Dave
You know, now that you mention it... I have noticed some things
Like, in meetings I noticed that Stan tends to kind of... steamroll some of the female employees
He never really seems to listen to them. And there was this one time when... Uh... Never mind..
You can tell me Dave. This is just between us.
Thanks, Dave. This has been very helpful.
Well... Alright. The other day Stan totally blew up at Sharon.
He told her that she needs to stop letting her "hormones interfere with her work."
She was so embarrassed... She left early that day.
Thanks, Dave. Thats good to know.
Anytime. Let me know if there's anything else I can do to help
